    1. Changing the COPYRIGHT_YEARS in vm_legal.h to 1998-2019
    2. COPYRIGHT_YEARS is used by UTF8_COPYRIGHT_STRING_BASE and
       UTF16_COPYRIGHT_STRING for win32 UTF-16 version.

