commit 13c49b85cebacea847d30c4e5a0b92fa7ea9dba8
Author: Oliver Kurth <okurth@vmware.com>
Date:   Tue Feb 6 16:32:37 2018 -0800

    hostinfo: Identify Amazon Linux
    
