Date:   Fri Sep 15 11:23:07 2017 -0700

    lib/file: Explcitly catch EIO in fileIOPosix.c
    
    No need to log as EIO is a known possibility.

commit 89ad718885b0141d3a0a46d34f164cb933830a1f
