    Bulk updates to the common-agent (CAF) code.

commit e5e137c279c3e69a509610b16e57548a04b4b9c0
Author: Oliver Kurth <okurth@vmware.com>
Date:   Fri Sep 15 11:22:46 2017 -0700

    Hgfs Win Client: fix PFD issues part II
