Date:   Tue Sep 17 20:19:21 2013 -0700

    Bump up tools version to 9.7.0.
    
    Signed-off-by: Dmitry Torokhov <dtor@vmware.com>

commit 036172f0cb580ca370a94324f6a465bcb71f2076
