	additional case-insensitivity fixes.

	* lib/include/hgfsBd.h, lib/include/hgfs.h,
	lib/include/hgfsProto.h: Add HGFS error code.
	
	* lib/hgfs/hgfsUtil.c, lib/guestInfo/Makefile.am,
